videos.description: Sun's Jonquel Jones throws a bad pass and it's picked up by Natasha Cloud who lays it in with ease.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Errant pass leads to Mystics’ layup) 2019/09/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Errant pass leads to Mystics' layup

videos.description: Kristi Toliver takes her defender off the dribble and puts in the tough layup right at the end of the first quarter.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Toliver puts in tough layup at the end of the 1st ) 2019/09/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Toliver puts in tough layup at the end of the 1st

videos.description: After the Sun cut the lead to 6, the Mystics use great ball movement to find Ariel Atkins who knocks down the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Atkins knocks down huge 3
